content: Hi, is here anyone using Hubot actively in production? What other bots are compatible, is there a plugins / bots marketplace like for zulip?

zulip@chat:~/roh$ bin/hubot --adapter zulip --name "myhubot"
npm WARN EBADENGINE Unsupported engine {
npm WARN EBADENGINE package: 'roh@0.0.0',
npm WARN EBADENGINE required: { node: '0.10.x' },
npm WARN EBADENGINE current: { node: 'v14.16.1', npm: '7.16.0' }
npm WARN EBADENGINE }
You can find many integrations on the integrations page: https://zulip.com/integrations/
